[SN]TITLE[SN]
Burundi crisis: 'Why I fled to Tanzania'

[SN]FIRST-SENTENCE[SN]
A year ago, Burundian President Pierre Nkurunziza announced he was running for a controversial third term in office.

[SN]RESTBODY[SN]
26 April 2016 Last updated at 16:28 BST
Protests followed, and in the ensuing crisis, hundreds have been killed and more than a quarter of a million people have fled the country.
Two refugees in Tanzania tell the BBC why they fled.
